    <description>Sends a periodic reminder to the Portal User if the portal information is not submitted yet. The Account Manager also gets assigned a task after 3 periods. The period is defined in Custom Meta Data Setting &quot;Telia Setting&quot;.</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
